class Solution:
    def maxOperations(self, s: str) -> int:
        # maximum: apply left to right 
        ones =0 
        ans = 0
        i=0
        while i < len(s):
            if s[i]=='1':
                ones+=1
                i+=1
                continue
            while i<len(s) and s[i]=='0': i+=1
            ans+=ones
        return ans
